---
/* Invoicing — Sección destacada de facturación electrónica SRI */
---

<section class="invoicing-section" id="invoicing">
  <!-- Línea decorativa con gradiente de marca -->
  <div class="brand-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="invoicing-grid">
      <!-- Columna izquierda: diagrama de flujo -->
      <div class="flow-diagram" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="flow-node">
          <div class="flow-circle">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-primary)" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M8 7h8M8 11h5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="flow-label">Tu empresa — Zelys ERP</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-line"><div class="flow-line-inner"></div></div>

        <div class="flow-node">
          <div class="flow-circle">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-secondary)" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><path d="M9 15l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="flow-label">Genera XML firmado electrónicamente</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-line"><div class="flow-line-inner"></div></div>

        <div class="flow-node">
          <div class="flow-circle">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-mint)" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="flow-label">SRI — Autorización en tiempo real</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-line"><div class="flow-line-inner"></div></div>

        <div class="flow-node">
          <div class="flow-circle">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-primary)" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22 6 12 13 2 6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="flow-label">Cliente — Recibe PDF + XML por email</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Columna derecha: copy -->
      <div class="invoicing-content">
        <span class="eyebrow">FACTURACIÓN ELECTRÓNICA · CERTIFICADO SRI</span>

        <h2>
          Emite cualquier comprobante<br/>electrónico en segundos.
        </h2>

        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>Facturas (nacionales y de exportación)</li>
          <li>Notas de crédito y débito</li>
          <li>Retenciones en la fuente e IVA</li>
          <li>Liquidaciones de compra de bienes</li>
          <li>Guías de remisión</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="invoicing-highlight">
          <span class="highlight-icon">📋</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Incluye firma electrónica integrada.</strong>
            Sin tokens físicos. Sin configuraciones complejas. Lista desde el primer día.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .invoicing-section {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-surface) 0%, var(--bg-base) 100%);
  }

  .brand-line {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gradient-brand);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .invoicing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Diagrama de flujo */
  .flow-diagram {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .flow-node {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .flow-circle {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--accent-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    position: relative;
  }

  .flow-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
    max-width: 200px;
  }

  .flow-line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 40px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .flow-line-inner {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent-primary), var(--accent-mint));
    animation: flow-pulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes flow-pulse {
    0% { transform: translateY(-100%); }
    50% { transform: translateY(0); }
    100% { transform: translateY(100%); }
  }

  /* Copy */
  .invoicing-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .invoicing-content h2 {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .invoicing-highlight {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--accent-primary-dim);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-active);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .invoicing-highlight strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .highlight-icon {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .invoicing-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    .flow-diagram {
      order: 2;
    }
    .invoicing-content {
      order: 1;
    }
  }
</style>
